00051 Entree& Perte_Charge_Circulaire_CoviMAC_Face::readOn(Entree& s )
00052 {
00053   Cerr << "Perte_Charge_Circulaire_CoviMAC_Face::readOn " << finl;
00054   sous_zone=false;
00055   int lambda_ortho_ok=0;
00056   int lambda_ok=0;
00057 // Definition des mots-cles
00058   Motcles les_mots(7);
00059   les_mots[0] = "lambda";
00060   les_mots[1] = "diam_hydr";
00061   les_mots[2] = "sous_zone";
00062   les_mots[3] = "direction";
00063   les_mots[4] = "lambda_ortho";
00064   les_mots[5] = "diam_hydr_ortho";
00065   les_mots[6] = "implicite";
00066 
00067 // Lecture et interpretation
00068   Motcle motlu, accolade_fermee="}", accolade_ouverte="{";
00069   s >> motlu;
00070   while (motlu != accolade_ouverte)
00071     {
00072       Cerr << "On attendait une { a la lecture d'un " << que_suis_je() << finl;
00073       Cerr << "et non : " << motlu << finl;
00074       exit();
00075     }
00076   s >> motlu;
00077   while (motlu != accolade_fermee)
00078     {
00079       int rang=les_mots.search(motlu);
00080       switch(rang)
00081         {
00082         case 0 :   //!< lambda
00083           {
00084             lambda_ok=1;
00085             Nom tmp;
00086             s >> tmp;
00087             Cerr << "Lecture et interpretation de la fonction " << tmp << " ... ";
00088             lambda.setNbVar(3+dimension);
00089             lambda.setString(tmp);
00090             lambda.addVar("Re_tot");
00091             lambda.addVar("Re_long");
00092             lambda.addVar("t");
00093             lambda.addVar("x");
00094             if (dimension>1)
00095               lambda.addVar("y");
00096             if (dimension>2)
00097               lambda.addVar("z");
00098             lambda.parseString();
00099             Cerr << " Ok" << finl;
00100             break;
00101           }
00102         case 1: //!< diam_hydr
00103           s >> diam_hydr;
00104           break;
00105         case 5: //!< diam_hydr_ortho
00106           s >> diam_hydr_ortho;
00107           break;
00108         case 2: //!< sous_zone
00109           s >> nom_sous_zone;
00110           sous_zone=true;
00111           break;
00112         case 3: //!< direction
00113           s >> v;
00114           break;
00115         case 4:   //!< lambda_ortho
00116           {
00117             lambda_ortho_ok=1;
00118             Nom tmp;
00119             s >> tmp;
00120             Cerr << "Lecture et interpretation de la fonction " << tmp << " ... ";
00121             lambda_ortho.setNbVar(3+dimension);
00122             lambda_ortho.setString(tmp);
00123             lambda_ortho.addVar("Re_tot");
00124             lambda_ortho.addVar("Re_ortho");
00125             lambda_ortho.addVar("t");
00126             lambda_ortho.addVar("x");
00127             if (dimension>1)
00128               lambda_ortho.addVar("y");
00129             if (dimension>2)
00130               lambda_ortho.addVar("z");
00131             lambda_ortho.parseString();
00132             Cerr << " Ok" << finl;
00133             break;
00134           }
00135         case 6:
00136           {
00137             s>>implicite_;
00138             break;
00139           }
00140         default : //!< non compris
00141           Cerr << "Mot cle \"" << motlu << "\" non compris lors de la lecture d'un "
00142                << que_suis_je() << finl;
00143           exit();
00144         }
00145       s >> motlu;
00146     }
00147 
00148 // Verification de la coherence
00149   if (lambda_ok==0)
00150     {
00151       Cerr << "Il faut definir l'expression lamba(Re_long,Re_tot)" << finl;
00152       exit();
00153     }
00154 
00155   if (lambda_ortho_ok==0)
00156     {
00157       Cerr << "Il faut definir l'expression lamba_ortho(Re_ortho,Re_tot)" << finl;
00158       exit();
00159     }
00160 
00161   if  ((!diam_hydr.non_nul())|| (diam_hydr->nb_comp()!=1))
00162     {
00163       Cerr << "Il faut definir le champ diam_hydr a une composante" << finl;
00164       exit();
00165     }
00166   if ((!diam_hydr_ortho.non_nul())|| (diam_hydr_ortho->nb_comp()!=1))
00167     {
00168       Cerr << "Il faut definir le champ diam_hydr_ortho a une composante" << finl;
00169       exit();
00170     }
00171   if (v->nb_comp()!=dimension)
00172     {
00173       Cerr << "Il faut definir le champ direction a " << dimension << " composantes" << finl;
00174       exit();
00175     }
00176 
00177 
00178   Cerr << "Fin de Perte_Charge_Circulaire_CoviMAC_Face::readOn" << finl;
00179   return s;
00180 }

00188 void  Perte_Charge_Circulaire_CoviMAC_Face::coeffs_perte_charge(const DoubleVect& u, const DoubleVect& pos,
00189                                                                 double t, double norme_u, double dh, double nu, double reynolds,double& coeff_ortho,double& coeff_long,double& u_l,DoubleVect& av_valeur) const
00190 {
00191 
00192 // calcul de dh_ortho
00193   double dh_ortho=diam_hydr_ortho->valeur_a_compo(pos,0);
00194 
00195 // calcul de u.d/||d||
00196 // Calcul de v et ||v||^2
00197   av_valeur.resize(dimension);
00198 
00199   v.valeur().valeur_a(pos,av_valeur);
00200 // on norme v
00201   {
00202     double vcarre=0;
00203     for (int dim=0; dim<dimension; dim++)
00204       vcarre+=av_valeur[dim]*av_valeur[dim];
00205     av_valeur/=sqrt(vcarre);
00206   }
00207 // Calcul de u.v/||v||
00208   u_l=0;
00209 
00210   for (int dim=0; dim<dimension; dim++)
00211     u_l+=u[dim]*av_valeur[dim];
00212 
00213   double u_ortho=sqrt(norme_u*norme_u-u_l*u_l);
00214   /* PL: To avoid a possible division by zero, we replace:
00215      double nu=norme_u*dh/reynolds;
00216 // calcule de Re_l et Re_ortho
00217 // Calcul du reynolds
00218      double Re_l=dabs(u_l)*dh/nu; */
00219 // By:
00220   double Re_l=dh*dabs(u_l)/nu;
00221   if(Re_l<1e-10) Re_l=1e-10;
00222 // PL: To avoid a possible division by zero, we replace:
00223   /* double Re_ortho=u_ortho*dh_ortho/nu; */
00224 // By:
00225   double Re_ortho=dh_ortho*u_ortho/nu;
00226   if (Re_ortho<1e-10) Re_ortho=1e-10;
00227 // Calcul de lambda
00228   lambda.setVar(0,reynolds);
00229   lambda.setVar(1,Re_l);
00230   lambda.setVar(2,t);
00231   lambda.setVar(3,pos[0]);
00232   if (dimension>1)
00233     lambda.setVar(4,pos[1]);
00234   if (dimension>2)
00235     lambda.setVar(5,pos[2]);
00236 
00237 // Calcul de lambda_ortho
00238   lambda_ortho.setVar(0,reynolds);
00239   lambda_ortho.setVar(1,Re_ortho);
00240   lambda_ortho.setVar(2,t);
00241   lambda_ortho.setVar(3,pos[0]);
00242   if (dimension>1)
00243     lambda_ortho.setVar(4,pos[1]);
00244   if (dimension>2)
00245     lambda_ortho.setVar(5,pos[2]);
00246   double l_ortho=lambda_ortho.eval(); //!< Pour ne pas evaluer 2 fois le parser
00247   double l_long=lambda.eval();
00248   coeff_ortho=l_ortho*u_ortho/2./dh_ortho;
00249   coeff_long=l_long *dabs(u_l)    /2./dh    ;
00250 }
